metadata.name: SOS 1
metadata.description:
Naples Pier, Naples Florida
September 29, 2022
One day after Hurricane Ian came on shore in Southwest Florida.

Southwest Florida has been devastated by Hurricane Ian. Prof Werder (aka The Nounish Professor) took this photo at the Naples Pier, the end of which was washed away. Someone had already written SOS in the sand.  

This edition will be available through October 3, 2022 and all proceeds will be donated to Hurricane Relief in Southwest Florida.  A POAP with receipt from donation will be sent to all holders.
